Trinity Mirror Merseyside, the Echo's parent company, is one of the North West’s largest multimedia providers reaching more than 900,000 adults every month. The Liverpool Echo, Trinity Mirror Merseyside’s flagship brand, is the area’s best-read newspaper including national newspapers. The Liverpool Echo reaches 1 in 3 people in the area with a daily readership of more than 256,000* people. The Liverpool Echo website reaches 1. 5 million unique users each month who look at around 8. 5 million pages**. To advertise with us please click here for full details. 